        <updateDate>2007-06-27T19:37:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fuel Efficiency Encouragement Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) repeal the limitation on the number of new qualified hybrid and advanced lean-burn technology vehicles eligible for the alternative motor vehicle tax credit; and (2) provide a tax credit for manufacturing new qualified hybrid motor vehicles.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
